"unik dan email valid untuk memastikan kamu memiliki kendali penuh atas kotak "
"masukmu."
msgstr ""
"Register yourself in just seconds. We only need a unique username and a "
"valid email to ensure you have full control over your inbox."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:128
msgid "Bagikan Link Kustom"
msgstr "Share Custom Link"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:129
msgid ""
"Dapatkan tautan unik seperti <code>curhatbox.my.id/username</code>. Bagikan "
"tautan ini ke Instagram Story, Bio TikTok, atau status WhatsApp untuk "
"mengundang teman-temanmu memberikan opini jujur."
msgstr ""
"Get a unique link like <code>curhatbox.my.id/username</code>. Share this "
"link to Instagram Stories, TikTok Bio, or WhatsApp status to invite your "
"friends to give honest opinions."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:135
msgid "Terima Pesan Anonim"
msgstr "Receive Anonymous Messages"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:136
msgid ""
"Terima pesan secara real-time. Kamu bisa membalasnya, memberikan reaksi "
"emoji, atau membagikan screenshot jawabanmu ke media sosial dengan desain "
"yang sudah kami siapkan agar tetap estetik."
msgstr ""
"Receive messages in real-time. You can reply to them, give emoji reactions, "
"or share screenshots of your answers to social media with designs we have "
"prepared to stay aesthetic."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:142
msgid "Misi Keamanan Kami"
msgstr "Our Safety Mission"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:144
msgid ""
"Di CurhatBox, kami percaya bahwa kebebasan berpendapat tidak boleh "
"mengorbankan kesehatan mental. Itulah sebabnya kami menerapkan algoritma "
"penyaringan kata-kata kasar secara otomatis. Setiap pesan yang masuk "
"melewati filter ketat untuk memastikan tidak ada perundungan (cyberbullying) "
"yang terjadi di platform kami."
msgstr ""
"At CurhatBox, we believe that freedom of speech should not sacrifice mental "
"health. That is why we implement an automatic harsh word filtering "
"algorithm. Every incoming message passes through strict filters to ensure no "
"cyberbullying occurs on our platform."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:147
msgid ""
"Selain itu, kami memberikan fitur <strong>Blokir IP</strong>. Jika ada oknum "
"yang menyalahgunakan anonimitas untuk menyerangmu, kamu bisa memblokir "
"mereka secara permanen agar mereka tidak bisa lagi mengirim pesan ke "
"profilmu selamanya."
msgstr ""
"In addition, we provide a <strong>Block IP</strong> feature. If someone "
"abuses anonymity to attack you, you can block them permanently so they can "
"no longer send messages to your profile forever."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:157
msgid "Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan (FAQ)"
msgstr "Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:162
msgid "Apakah CurhatBox benar-benar anonim?"
msgstr "Is CurhatBox really anonymous?"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:163
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Ya, 100%%. Kami tidak menyimpan data pribadi pengirim selain alamat IP untuk "
"keperluan keamanan (anti-spam). Penerima tidak akan pernah tahu siapa "
"pengirimnya kecuali pengirim itu sendiri yang memberitahu."
msgstr ""
"Yes, 100%%. We do not store any personal data of the sender other than the "
"IP address for security purposes (anti-spam). The recipient will never know "
"who the sender is unless the sender tells them."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:166
msgid "Bagaimana cara kerja fitur Pesan Sekali Baca?"
msgstr "How does the One-Time Read Message feature work?"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:167
msgid ""
"Mode <em>Self-Destruct</em> memastikan pesan akan terhapus dari server "
"segera setelah penerima membukanya untuk pertama kalinya. Ini adalah "
"perlindungan privasi tingkat tinggi dari kami."
msgstr ""
"<em>Self-Destruct</em> mode ensures the message will be deleted from the "
"server as soon as the recipient opens it for the first time. This is high-"
"level privacy protection from us."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:172
msgid "Bagaimana cara membagikan link ke Instagram?"
msgstr "How to share the link to Instagram?"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:173
msgid ""
"Buka dasbor Anda, salin link profil, lalu gunakan fitur 'Stiker Tautan' di "
"Instagram Story. Tempelkan link Anda di sana dan tunggu pesan masuk!"
msgstr ""
"Open your dashboard, copy your profile link, then use the 'Link Sticker' "
"feature on Instagram Stories. Paste your link there and wait for messages to "
"come in!"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:176
msgid "Bagaimana jika saya menerima pesan kasar?"
msgstr "What if I receive harsh messages?"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:177
msgid ""
"Anda bisa langsung memblokir pengirim tersebut menggunakan fitur 'Blokir IP' "
"yang ada di bawah setiap pesan yang Anda terima."
msgstr ""
"You can immediately block the sender using the 'Block IP' feature found "
"under every message you receive."

